Title: Establishes the practice of telepharmacy
Summary: Establishes the practice of telepharmacy to allow for the practice of pharmacy provided by a pharmacist to one or more remote site pharmacies in which all sites are connected via computer link, video link and audio link, or other functionally equivalent telecommunications equipment.

ActClause: AN ACT to amend the education law, in relation to establishing the practice of telepharmacy
